---
title: Protein Packed Turkey Stir-Fry with Carrots and Pepper
description: Quick, healthy and easy to prep, our flash-in-the-pan turkey stir-fry is the perfect recipe for busy evenings. Super lean and packed with protein, turkey is a great addition to this weeknight favourite and works brilliantly with the rich umami flavours in this dish. Crunchy carrot and red peppers (packed with Vitamin C) give the dish a lovely texture, whilst ginger and red chilli give it a welcome kick of heat. Serve in bowls, top with chopped spring onion, and dig in!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/protein-packed-turkey-stir-fry-9649b091-f4a5de1a.jpg
